{"tid":341850,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬到上海","createTime":"2017-07-31T06:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T08:57:36.000Z","uid":16666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aea0a2132a04c3e939c86a621a4586ad58d1160a","tid":341850,"uid":16666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"尼馬轉會傳聞繼續吹，係咪真係去巴黎聖日耳門，球迷仲要拭目以待。不過佢本人就唔理咁多住，今朝飛抵中國上海，喺微博度同網民打招呼之餘，仲徵求意見問下嚟到上海有乜好做。<br />\n巴塞隆拿完成喺美國嘅國冠盃賽事之後，大軍就飛返歐洲，不過尼馬就獲准都時離隊，自己飛去中國。今次佢係以私人名義去中國，未透露有乜行程同活動。尼馬都好識做，到步後喺佢微博到放段片，兼且出段中英對照嘅文同球迷打招呼，仲問球迷喺上海有乜好做，不妨畀啲意見佢。<br />\n尼馬微博文章節錄：<br />\n你好，中國！我是尼馬，我來中國了！現在上海，我要擁抱我的中國球迷們，感謝你們的支持。朋友們，希望你們能給我提些建議，告訴我在上海我該做些什麼 。致敬！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20170731/57022974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20170731%2F57022974&d=EHHoFwyMeaEsIlng%2BayXz26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=94692ecd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20170731%2F57022974&h=ae69c364\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20170731/57022974</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尼馬係條片講SHI那 定 支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9a4d199e20e8cf4b25c5f682f45a01970399cc","tid":341850,"uid":70201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:40:42.000Z","msg":"躝"},{"pid":"987e81e25f4f231ab8849fb9cb84cfd1a4a1bcd0","tid":341850,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"叫雞同selfie"},{"pid":"fbdaf7d051b2f4156b38fe3efd54f5c58d75cfb6","tid":341850,"uid":17853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"去探hulk 啦"},{"pid":"9b65d4363c2356613e7538301ef4d2758522c27f","tid":341850,"uid":47584,